title: 'Survivor,' Season 42, Episode 5 With Eliza Orlins
description:
Riley and Juliet are joined by 'Survivor: Vanuatu' and 'Survivor: Micronesia' contestant, Eliza Orlins. They discuss how their opinions are changing about Jonathan and break down the confusing Tribal Council vote. Plus, Eliza talks about her experiences on 'Survivor' and what she thinks of the new twists.
Hosts: Riley McAtee and Juliet Litman
Guest: Eliza Orlins
Production: Carlos Chiriboga
